driver

Class Driver

  • java.lang.Object
    • driver.Driver

  • public class Driver
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to speak to all motors of the robot. With this class you can say the robot has to turn his wheels and range sensor.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Timon van den Brink, Scott Mackay

      • turnAngle

        public static void turnAngle(int angle,
                             int speed)
        Turns the robot a given amount of degrees and stops it. While turning the method sleeps. That means the thread that called this method won't continue until the robot has turned the amount of degrees and stopped turning.
        Parameters:
        angle - the angle that the robot has to turn.
        speed - the speed of the robot turning in cm/s.

      • driveSmoothLeft

        Parameters:

        speed - the speed of the robot driving the arc.
